WEBVTT

00:00:29.004 --> 00:00:33.706
Ja prethodim ratu protiv naših bližnjih,
mislim, ratu protiv droga.

00:00:33.730 --> 00:00:35.213
Prethodim svemu tome.

00:00:35.855 --> 00:00:37.009
Prethodim toliko,

00:00:37.033 --> 00:00:38.816
prošao sam kroz plime i oseke

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:41.207
i prošao sam kroz dobra i loša vremena,

00:00:41.231 --> 00:00:45.389
i dalje definitivno volim
što sam policajac.

00:00:46.207 --> 00:00:49.958
Volim da budem policajac jer je to
uvek bio moj poziv,

00:00:49.982 --> 00:00:51.362
a nikad posao.

00:00:52.219 --> 00:00:53.584
Čak i s tim,

00:00:54.538 --> 00:00:58.814
moja lična tajna jeste
da je policija u krizi.

00:00:59.616 --> 00:01:01.130
U nevidljivoj krizi,